{"post_stream":{"posts":[{"id":37785,"name":"","username":"UrhoIsTheBest","avatar_template":"https://avatars.discourse-cdn.com/v4/letter/u/7feea3/{size}.png","created_at":"2020-05-31T07:39:28.862Z","cooked":"\u003cp\u003eThere are very few posts discussing about multiple terrains neighboring each other (e.g. a very old \u003ca href=\"https://discourse.urho3d.io/t/terrain-stitching/2191\"\u003epost\u003c/a\u003e).\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch1\u003eProblem\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNow I am trying to make two terrains adjacent to each other.\u003cbr\u003e\nI found there are very small glitches (narrow gaps) at the boundary.\u003cbr\u003e\nFor example:\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/original/2X/4/46e0688104d8c11eab55c57cea3db7c967da6b74.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/a70dlHokMNaWqIuTHHoOCYTVsdS.jpeg?dl=1\" title=\"Screen Shot 2020-05-31 at 00.22.13\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/4/46e0688104d8c11eab55c57cea3db7c967da6b74_2_629x500.jpeg\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2020-05-31 at 00.22.13\" data-base62-sha1=\"a70dlHokMNaWqIuTHHoOCYTVsdS\" width=\"629\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/4/46e0688104d8c11eab55c57cea3db7c967da6b74_2_629x500.jpeg, https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/4/46e0688104d8c11eab55c57cea3db7c967da6b74_2_943x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/4/46e0688104d8c11eab55c57cea3db7c967da6b74_2_1258x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/4/46e0688104d8c11eab55c57cea3db7c967da6b74_2_10x10.png\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cuse xlink:href=\"#far-image\"\u003e\u003c/use\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003cspan class=\"filename\"\u003eScreen Shot 2020-05-31 at 00.22.13\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"informations\"\u003e2272×1804 944 KB\u003c/span\u003e\u003csvg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cuse xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"\u003e\u003c/use\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nand\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/original/2X/0/0ffdef6e8d30b50c335af394172812d877b73c0c.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/2htdnRL7iyquXnnxT1yyl6qtK8I.jpeg?dl=1\" title=\"Screen Shot 2020-05-31 at 00.25.30\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/0/0ffdef6e8d30b50c335af394172812d877b73c0c_2_629x500.jpeg\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2020-05-31 at 00.25.30\" data-base62-sha1=\"2htdnRL7iyquXnnxT1yyl6qtK8I\" width=\"629\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/0/0ffdef6e8d30b50c335af394172812d877b73c0c_2_629x500.jpeg, https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/0/0ffdef6e8d30b50c335af394172812d877b73c0c_2_943x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/0/0ffdef6e8d30b50c335af394172812d877b73c0c_2_1258x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/0/0ffdef6e8d30b50c335af394172812d877b73c0c_2_10x10.png\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cuse xlink:href=\"#far-image\"\u003e\u003c/use\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003cspan class=\"filename\"\u003eScreen Shot 2020-05-31 at 00.25.30\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"informations\"\u003e2272×1804 866 KB\u003c/span\u003e\u003csvg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cuse xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"\u003e\u003c/use\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI don’t think it’s a simple shift due to wrong coordinates.\u003cbr\u003e\nIf set camera to FILL_WIREFRAME mode\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cpre\u003e\u003ccode class=\"lang-auto\"\u003e  camera-\u0026gt;SetFillMode(FILL_WIREFRAME);\n\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI also noticed the mesh seems not continuous.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/original/2X/6/61cfe620c5dd604807f171e387f81836b4d05de6.png\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/dXhJDo3bXjuAuGbNDGVRnvev7Lw.png?dl=1\" title=\"Screen Shot 2020-05-31 at 00.27.14\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/6/61cfe620c5dd604807f171e387f81836b4d05de6_2_629x500.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2020-05-31 at 00.27.14\" data-base62-sha1=\"dXhJDo3bXjuAuGbNDGVRnvev7Lw\" width=\"629\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/6/61cfe620c5dd604807f171e387f81836b4d05de6_2_629x500.png, https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/6/61cfe620c5dd604807f171e387f81836b4d05de6_2_943x750.png 1.5x, https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/6/61cfe620c5dd604807f171e387f81836b4d05de6_2_1258x1000.png 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/6/61cfe620c5dd604807f171e387f81836b4d05de6_2_10x10.png\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cuse xlink:href=\"#far-image\"\u003e\u003c/use\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003cspan class=\"filename\"\u003eScreen Shot 2020-05-31 at 00.27.14\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"informations\"\u003e2272×1804 1.24 MB\u003c/span\u003e\u003csvg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cuse xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"\u003e\u003c/use\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch1\u003eCode\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMy sample code:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cpre\u003e\u003ccode class=\"lang-auto\"\u003e Node* terrain_node_center = scene_-\u0026gt;CreateChild(\"TerrainCenter\");\n  Terrain* terrain_center = terrain_node_center-\u0026gt;CreateComponent\u0026lt;Terrain\u0026gt;();\n\n  const float size = 204.8;\n  Node* terrain_node_east = scene_-\u0026gt;CreateChild(\"TerrainEast\");\n  terrain_node_east-\u0026gt;SetPosition(Vector3(size, 0, 0));\n  Terrain* terrain_east = terrain_node_east-\u0026gt;CreateComponent\u0026lt;Terrain\u0026gt;();\n\n  Node* terrain_node_west = scene_-\u0026gt;CreateChild(\"TerrainWest\");\n  terrain_node_west-\u0026gt;SetPosition(Vector3(-size, 0, 0));\n  Terrain* terrain_west = terrain_node_west-\u0026gt;CreateComponent\u0026lt;Terrain\u0026gt;();\n\n  Node* terrain_node_north = scene_-\u0026gt;CreateChild(\"TerrainNorth\");\n  terrain_node_north-\u0026gt;SetPosition(Vector3(0, 0, size));\n  Terrain* terrain_north = terrain_node_north-\u0026gt;CreateComponent\u0026lt;Terrain\u0026gt;();\n\n  Node* terrain_node_south = scene_-\u0026gt;CreateChild(\"TerrainSouth\");\n  terrain_node_south-\u0026gt;SetPosition(Vector3(0, 0, -size));\n  Terrain* terrain_south = terrain_node_south-\u0026gt;CreateComponent\u0026lt;Terrain\u0026gt;();\n\n  std::vector\u0026lt;Terrain*\u0026gt; terrains{terrain_center, terrain_east, terrain_west, terrain_north, terrain_south};\n  for (auto* terrain : terrains) {\n    terrain-\u0026gt;SetSpacing(Vector3(0.1, 0.2, 0.1));\n    terrain-\u0026gt;SetSmoothing(true);\n\n//    terrain-\u0026gt;SetMaterial(cache-\u0026gt;GetResource\u0026lt;Material\u0026gt;(\"Materials/Terrain.xml\"));\n    terrain-\u0026gt;SetCastShadows(true);\n    terrain-\u0026gt;SetOccluder(true);\n  }\n\n  terrain_center-\u0026gt;SetHeightMap(cache-\u0026gt;GetResource\u0026lt;Image\u0026gt;(\"Textures/TestTerrainCenter.png\"));\n  terrain_east-\u0026gt;SetHeightMap(cache-\u0026gt;GetResource\u0026lt;Image\u0026gt;(\"Textures/TestTerrainEast.png\"));\n  terrain_west-\u0026gt;SetHeightMap(cache-\u0026gt;GetResource\u0026lt;Image\u0026gt;(\"Textures/TestTerrainWest.png\"));\n  terrain_north-\u0026gt;SetHeightMap(cache-\u0026gt;GetResource\u0026lt;Image\u0026gt;(\"Textures/TestTerrainNorth.png\"));\n  terrain_south-\u0026gt;SetHeightMap(cache-\u0026gt;GetResource\u0026lt;Image\u0026gt;(\"Textures/TestTerrainSouth.png\"));\n\n // I tried both setting and not setting neighbor, no difference.\n  terrain_center-\u0026gt;SetEastNeighbor(terrain_east);\n  terrain_east-\u0026gt;SetWestNeighbor(terrain_center);\n\n  terrain_center-\u0026gt;SetNorthNeighbor(terrain_north);\n  terrain_north-\u0026gt;SetSouthNeighbor(terrain_center);\n\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\u003ch1\u003eHeightmap\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMy heightmap is 2049*2049 (2^n + 1).\u003cbr\u003e\nI also made sure the edge pixels of two images are the same (e.g. 2049 pixel for 2048 size).\u003cbr\u003e\nAlso attached example heightmaps:\u003cbr\u003e\nTestTerrainCenter.png\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/original/2X/1/190713eff31797682a3354b823384accf044ee7c.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/3zp6gqTCHu6OeV0QhZTARPVlzli.jpeg?dl=1\" title=\"TestTerrainCenter\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/1/190713eff31797682a3354b823384accf044ee7c_2_500x500.jpeg\" alt=\"TestTerrainCenter\" data-base62-sha1=\"3zp6gqTCHu6OeV0QhZTARPVlzli\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/1/190713eff31797682a3354b823384accf044ee7c_2_500x500.jpeg, https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/1/190713eff31797682a3354b823384accf044ee7c_2_750x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/1/190713eff31797682a3354b823384accf044ee7c_2_1000x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/1/190713eff31797682a3354b823384accf044ee7c_2_10x10.png\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cuse xlink:href=\"#far-image\"\u003e\u003c/use\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003cspan class=\"filename\"\u003eTestTerrainCenter\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"informations\"\u003e2049×2049 483 KB\u003c/span\u003e\u003csvg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cuse xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"\u003e\u003c/use\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nTestTerrainNorth.png\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/original/2X/8/87683430c6271a4af8fe64a8797fd08631a5419d.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/jjRIhEJsLF0SIEJY3ysou7ZJ4Dj.jpeg?dl=1\" title=\"TestTerrainNorth\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/8/87683430c6271a4af8fe64a8797fd08631a5419d_2_500x500.jpeg\" alt=\"TestTerrainNorth\" data-base62-sha1=\"jjRIhEJsLF0SIEJY3ysou7ZJ4Dj\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/8/87683430c6271a4af8fe64a8797fd08631a5419d_2_500x500.jpeg, https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/8/87683430c6271a4af8fe64a8797fd08631a5419d_2_750x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://global.di